commit.message:
re PR c++/53503 ([C++0x] unexpected AST of kind ltgt_expr)

gcc/cp
2012-05-28  Paolo Carlini  <paolo.carlini@oracle.com>

	PR c++/53503
	* semantics.c (potential_constant_expression_1): Handle LTGT_EXPR.

libstdc++-v3
2012-05-28  Paolo Carlini  <paolo.carlini@oracle.com>

	PR c++/53503
	* testsuite/26_numerics/headers/cmath/53503.cc: New.

From-SVN: r187928

+	PR c++/53503

+
 2012-05-26  Paolo Carlini  <paolo.carlini@oracle.com>
 
 	PR c++/53491

@@ -8487,6 +8487,7 @@ potential_constant_expression_1 (tree t, bool want_rval, tsubst_flags_t flags)
     case UNGT_EXPR:
     case UNGE_EXPR:
     case UNEQ_EXPR:
+    case LTGT_EXPR:
     case RANGE_EXPR:
     case COMPLEX_EXPR:
       want_rval = true;
